      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Most esteemed Oberstudienrath, ¶  ¶ Enclosed I am returning the letter from Dr Sonder ¶  with sincere thanks. ¶  ¶ Regarding the wish expressed in it concerning the motivation for the said distinction...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M71.09.15</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Gustav von Silcher to Ferdinand von Krauss</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Staatliches Museum für Naturkunde, Stuttgart.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Verehrtester Herr OStRath!<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Oberstudienrath.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Im Anschluss gebe ich den Brief von Herrn Dr Sonder mit verbindlichstem Dank zurück.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Betreffend den darin ausgedrückten Wunsch wegen der Motivirung der fraglichen Auszeichnung, so wird sich hiewegen wohl nichts mehr machen lassen, nachdem dem Herrn v Müller sowohl vom Minist. d. Ausw., als von hier aus das entsprechende Dokument zugefertigt worden ist.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In der That sind es aber <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">für uns</hi>
               </seg> doch nur die beträchtl. <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Schenkungen</hi>
               </seg>, welche zu der fragl Auszeichnung veranlasst haben, nicht die sonstigen Verdienste v Müllers.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Nach meiner Ansicht könnten letztere höchstens noch in einem <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">öffentl Artikel</hi>
               </seg> neben den Schenkungen erwähnt werden</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit freundlichster Empfehlung</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr ergebenster</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Silcher</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Den 15 Sptb 71.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Most esteemed Oberstudienrath,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Enclosed I am returning the letter from Dr Sonder<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See W. Sonder to F. von Krauss, 17 August 1871 (in this edition as M71-08-17), in which he passed on M's wishes to have his various scientific merits recognised in the certificate of his elevation to the rank of hereditary Baron ['Freiherr']; cf. also M to F. von Krauss, 8 October 1871, in which he expressed the same wish.</p>
               </note> with sincere thanks.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Regarding the wish expressed in it concerning the motivation for the said distinction, it is unlikely that anything can be done about this any more, as the relevant document has been forwarded by the Foreign Minister as well as from here to Mr von Mueller.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>But indeed <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">for us</hi>
               </seg> it is only the considerable <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">donations</hi>
               </seg> that motivated the said distinction, not von Mueller's other merits.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In my view the latter could at best only be mentioned in a published notice together with the donations.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With my sincerest commendations</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most humble</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Silcher.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">15 September 1871.</p>
         </div>
